scuss each process in light of the\ntypical range of stellar densities observed for star-forming regions. I finish\nby discussing these effects in the context of theories for the birth\nenvironment of the Solar System.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 15 Jul 2020 18:00:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-07-17"}
