 phrasing the inversion\nproblem as a particular optimization problem.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 15 Jul 2020 18:00:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 28 Jan 2021 13:22:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-01-29"}
