ial capital to make them support crisis measurement of the\ncompany most effectively while keeping their turnover intention low.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 15 Jul 2020 19:36:51 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 19 Jul 2020 12:57:35 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 23 Jul 2020 14:24:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-02-15"}
