Agg achieves over 20% gains in terms of communication and\nenergy cost reduction compared to several baseline designs within at most 1% of\naccuracy loss.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 16 Jul 2020 09:32:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-07-17"}
