 is given to agents and\n$|\\Lambda_{all}|=O(|\\Lambda_{good}|)$ holds.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 16 Jul 2020 09:43:47 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 1 Aug 2020 09:21:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-08-04"}
